[18.900426, "o", "    /events [filter] [query]\u001b[2m   search feed: all / watch / milestones / messages\u001b[22m\r\n    /find <text>\u001b[2m   search the current event buffer\u001b[22m\r\n    /cancel\u001b[2m   stop waiting for the current Manager reply\u001b[22m\r\n    /task <text>\u001b[2m   queue work directly\u001b[22m\r\n    /plan <objective>\u001b[2m   preview a Planner-authored execution plan\u001b[22m\r\n    /nudge <text>\u001b[2m   inject guidance into the running mission\u001b[22m\r\n    /note <text>\u001b[2m   append a manual note to the timeline\u001b[22m\r\n    /done <id>\u001b[2m   mark a task done\u001b[22m\r\n    /skip <id>\u001b[2m   skip a task\u001b[22m\r\n    /stop <id>\u001b[2m   stop a task's auto-iteration\u001b[22m\r\n    /item <id>\u001b[2m   inspect a full task contract\u001b[22m\r\n    /run\u001b[2m   return to the always-live mission feed\u001b[22m\r\n    /new [objective]\u001b[2m   review, create, and switch to a fresh conversation\u001b[22m\r\n    /daemons [query]\u001b[2m   find every session + switch or create\u001b[22m\r\n    /resume [list|<id>]\u001b[2m   switch to another project/session\u001b[22m\r\n    /attach <id|prefix>\u001b[2m   follow another project (read the stream)\u001b[22m\r\n    /doctor\u001b[2m   diagnose 'why isn't anything running'\u001b[22m\r\n    /backend [codex|claude|copilot]\u001b[2m   view or change the shared runner backend\u001b[22m\r\n    /config [key=value …]\u001b[2m   view or change runtime settings\u001b[22m\r\n    /identity [set <text>]\u001b[2m   view or replace the operator identity card\u001b[22m\r\n    /reset\u001b[2m   drop the warm Manager conversation context\u001b[22m\r\n    /skills [ls|promote <name>]\u001b[2m   inspect or promote runtime skills\u001b[22m\r\n    /clear\u001b[2m   clear the event feed view\u001b[22m\r\n    /reconnect\u001b[2m   reconnect the live event stream\u001b[22m\r\n    /help\u001b[2m   keys + full command reference\u001b[22m\r\n    /quit\u001b[2m   leave the cockpit